title: DNSK_vs_DJ_Venom-Probability_Theory-2015
description:
DESCRIPTION:

This vocal-/psy trance DJ mix is a collaboration between DNSK (Sweden) and DJ Venom (Israel). 

It starts off with about an hour of vocal trance - mixed by DNSK - to then head over to the dark side - with psy trance delivered by DJ Venom - the second hour.


Title: DNSK vs. DJ Venom - Probability Theory
Content: Music
Type: DJ Mix
Genre: Vocal-/Psy Trance
Year: 2015
Format: MP3
Bitrate: 320 kbps

BIO:

DNSK was set to walk Earth 33 years ago and resides in the land of Swedes where the sun in the northern parts never rises during the winter. He has been a DJ since 1994 and produces DJ mixes as well as audiovisual art in the form of music videos along with them. His interests in life includes music from various styles and genres along with sound- and visual art in all forms and shapes, though mainly - besides abstract compositions and pop art/lowbrow - surrealism, which he finds pleasing to the mind on many levels. Nothing less, but maybe more - a question of interest.

DJ Venom combines the eclectic sounds of Electronic Music with many different music genres to bring a truly unique sound to the dance floor.
